title: Sesame Roasted Chicken Salad with Pear and Creamy Wasabi Dressing
description: Tonight's dish is designed to tantalize your taste buds! Sesame chicken, sweet pear, crunchy kale mix and punchy wasabi dressing mingle together in this umami-packed weeknight wonder.

